Description:
OFFICER'S BEST TOWNHOUSE COULD BE YOURS!
"Officer's best set of townhouses."
In the thriving estate of Arena comes this townhouse with only one neighbouring property. Backing on to parkland the townhouse at 18 Manna Row is positioned within walking distance to shops, schools and public transport.
The owners have been proud to call this their family home and they are hoping you too can enjoy everything this affordable townhouse has to offer.
Featuring:
- Three bedrooms, master with walk-in robe, en-suite and park-facing aspect;
- Second bedroom with walk-in robe and balcony, perfect for the independent child;
- Two individual living zones plus a sizeable dining area;
- Modern and bright kitchen overlooking the dining and family room;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double garage with two separate roller doors and internal access;
- Gorgeous decked patio overlooking the parkland.

IMMERSE YOURSELF IN TRENDY ARENA
"Be apart of the trending Arena Estate for a fraction of the expected price."
Located within walking distance to the versatile Arena shopping centre and Cardinia Train station is a beautifully presented three bedroom home perfect for the first home buyer, investor or downsizer.
Featuring:
- Three bedrooms, master with walk-in robe and en-suite;
- Study;
- Formal sitting room removed from the open plan living/dining area;
- Well-appointed kitchen with all the mod cons you could expect to discover in a modern house;
- Ducted heating and split system cooling;
- Garage with internal and remote control access;
- Quaint courtyard adorning the backyard;
- Landscaped both front and back.
View for yourself.

BLANK CANVAS IN A HOT AREA
"Begin your dream experience in the vibrant estate of Potter's Grove."
Presented in the sought after Potters Grove Estate, this near-new home (one year) will leave you breathless.
Located only a few minutes drive from all major amenities, primary and secondary schools, Officer train station, shopping complex and sporting facilities.
Set on approximately 448m2 this home features;
- Four bedrooms, master complete with walk in robe and ensuite with double vanity and oversized shower;
- Study;
- Formal living, dining, lounge and theatre room;
- Gorgeous kitchen with 900mm stainless steel appliances; walk in pantry, great bench and storage space plus feature lighting;
- Heating and cooling throughout;
- Alfresco overlooking the backyard.
